Module kivakit.core
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.language.reflection

Class Type<T>

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.language.reflection.Type<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.Named
public class Type<T> extends Object implements com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.Named
Reflects on a class and retains a set of Property objects that can be used to efficiently set property values.
